In this episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah, Bhide and Jethalal select their teams for Gokuldham Premier League (GPL). All the society members start preparing for the match. It is also decided that the losing captain will clean the society with the help of a broom. 

Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Episode - 176
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #livcomedy #tmkoc #taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #‡§§‡§æ‡§∞‡§ï‡§Æ‡•á‡§π‡§§‡§æ‡§ï‡§æ‡§â‡§≤‡•ç‡§ü‡§æ‡§ö‡§∂‡•ç‡§Æ‡§æ 

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal‚Äôs Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Click here to watch all the fun episodes of TMKOC - Revisit The Journey: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLSXTaG1fT0cSkLfD49YxG8YsjmWdKNU0r

Tere Bin Episode 46 - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream - 18th May 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Tere Bin Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab‚Äôs life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family‚Äôs decision regarding her and Murtasim‚Äôs life. Meerab‚Äôs hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab‚Äôs arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim‚Äôs family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

snippet.title: PART 1 - RAHUL DUA IN AMERICA - TIMEZONES, TAP WATER & COSTCO | StandUp Comedy by Rahul Dua | USA
snippet.description:
EDIT:  "Oh Hello!" Australia and NZ tour (Jun'23) tickets: https://linktr.ee/RahulDuaTour
"New Comedy Special 2023-24" UK-EU Tour (Aug-Sep'23) tickets: https://linktr.ee/RahulDuaTour

This video was shot in Boston, Massachusetts on 25th March, 2023. 
It was my first ever visit to the USA and I am very exited to present to you some of my favourite observations & experiences from the days I spent in the US as part of my Stand Up World Tour. 
These are observational jokes rehearsed and delivered in 12-13 shows, unlike conventional stand up content which takes a couple of years to perfect. So need all your love, appreciation and support as I deal with timezone differences, the concept of drinkable tap water and Costco as the one stop shop for all possible needs. Drop in a LIKE and SHARE the video if you've had similar experiences or know someone who went through something similar, and COMMENT with your favourite joke from the video. 
Part 2 out soon, so stay tuned!

snippet.title: Kya Loge Tum | Akshay Kumar | Amyra Dastur | BPraak | Jaani | Arvindr Khaira | Zohrajabeen
snippet.description:
Desi Melodies presents in association with Cape Of Good Films & Azeem Dayani the first single, 'Kya Loge Tum,' from B Praak's highly anticipated debut album, "Zohrajabeen." The star-studded team of B Praak, Jaani, Arvindr Khaira, and Akshay Kumar reunites for the first time since the pop-culture-defining songs 'Filhall' and 'Filhaal 2.'

The emotionally charged lyrics written by Jaani, along with his heart-wrenching composition, add an extra layer of depth to the already powerful track produced by B Praak himself. Arvindr Khaira takes it to the next level with his visionary direction, featuring Akshay Kumar and Amyra Dastur's palpable chemistry that will leave you wanting more.

Listen to 'Kya Loge Tum' - https://bit.ly/KyaLogeTum

Tere Bin Episode 47 Teaser - 18th May 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab‚Äôs life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family‚Äôs decision regarding her and Murtasim‚Äôs life. Meerab‚Äôs hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab‚Äôs arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim‚Äôs family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

snippet.title: Phir Aur Kya Chahiye| Zara Hatke Zara Bachke| Vicky K, Sara Ali K, Arijit Singh,Sachin-Jigar,Amitabh
snippet.description:
Lose yourself in the magic of love with the much-awaited song "Phir Aur Kya Chahiye'' from the film 'Zara Hatke Zara Bachke'. Mesmerizing vocals of Arijit Singh perfectly complement the intense chemistry between Sara Ali Khan and Vicky Kaushal. The music is composed by the talented duo Sachin-Jigar, and is here to make your heart skip a beat!

The soulful lyrics penned by Amitabh Bhattacharya will make you feel the love. A must watch movie directed by Laxman Utekar, featuring Sara Ali Khan and Vicky Kaushal.

Show Name ‚Äì Maddam Sir
Star Cast ‚Äì Gulki Joshi, Shilpa Shinde, Yukti Kapoor, Sonali Naik, Bhavika Sharma, Pankhuri Awasthy Rode, Priyanshu Singh, and Ajay Jadhav
Produced By ‚Äì Jay Mehta

#MaddamSir #‡§Æ‡•à‡§°‡•ç‡§°‡§Æ‡§∏‡§∞ #comedy 

About The Show:
-----------------------------
Set in Lucknow the show is based in one such all-women Police station made by 4 beautiful quirky women. Pushpa, the oldest of them, is the head constable who tries to balance her life between home and work. Karishma, the Sub Inspector, is fish out of the water as she is at loggerheads with the philosophy of the police station. She beats before she talks but now she has to solve all cases through reconciliation. Santosh Sharma is a young new recruit and a typical lonely girl in the city. The head of the pack is S.H.O Haseena Mallik, witty, romantic leads by example. The common challenge for all these women is to bring sensitivity to their policing while dealing with cases that come to this police station. Hence their solution is most unusual. The characters and the cases add to the fun and humor of the show. While Pushpa and Karishma are the saas-bahu duo, who keep us entertained by their Squabbles, it is Haseena - Karishma's ideological differences that add to the drama madam and comedy

snippet.description:

snippet.title: Anuv Jain - ANTARIKSH (Official Video)
snippet.description:
The tenth studio recorded single, written, sung and composed by #AnuvJain is here!

Antariksh out now on all streaming platforms : https://anuvjain.lnk.to/Antariksh

For inquiries - anuvjain.work@gmail.com
Instagram - @anuvjain
Manager- aayushman@representmgmt.in

MUSIC PRODUCTION: Angad Singh Bahra & Somanshu Agarwal
DIRECTOR: Maan Boruah
ASST. DIRECTOR: Paras Kumar
CREATIVE PRODUCER: Maan Boruah, Paras Kumar
CINEMATOGRAPHY: Maan Boruah
2ND DOP: Karan
CAMERA FIRST ASST.: Raja
CAMERA SECOND ASST.: Amar
GAFFER: Jai Singh
ART DIRECTOR: Vikas Kumar
ART TEAM: Raminder, Aadi, Subod, Vikram, Munazir, Anish, Kadir, Manoj
LINE PRODUCER: Manohar Kamat
TECH PARTNER: Mount Everest Media
POST PRODUCTION: The Last Slice Studios
VFX ARTIST: Sushant 
SPOT: Sarvar, Karan, Vishwajeet
MAKEUP: Khyati Nagi, Kiran
BTS: Rishita Sharma
CAST COORDINATORS: Rea Kwatra, Shivansh Anand
SUPPORTING CAST: Tanu Awasthy, Shubhangi Bhadani, Niharika Arora, Pavani Jain, Kiyomi, Jiya, Panchoy Baruah, Namrata Singha, Bornali kramsapi , Priyanka Roy, Stanzin Kunsal, Maisha Bagchi, Mishti Raghuvanshi, Samaira Malik, Neeranjana Tiwari, Aalya Malik, Nipun Thapliyal
STYLING: Robertson lyngdoh 
STYLING ASSISTANT: Prerna Sharma 
DRESS DADA: Nishank Kumar 
CLOTHES: @Garuda_SS
JEWELRY: @dashia.in

Antariksh Lyrics

Para 1

Karta mein baatein meri 
Aaine se dekho teri
Tujhse kaise 
Khul ke waise
Bolun mein yeh raaz dil ke?

Ab tere samne hoon 
Kitna kuch mein kehna chahoon
Mujhko yeh bata de fir kyun
Khojun mein alfaaz milke?

Dekho yeh aaina 
Aye na tu kyun yahan?
Aaine mein saath mere
Teri hi toh hai jagah

Uljha hoon alfazon mein hi 
Nikle na awazon mein ki 
Pass mere 
Pass mein aaja
Aa ja na  

Chorus 

Aa re aa x 8

Para 2

Tere sitaron mein yaan 
Ik tara hazaron mein kya?
Mere inn sawalon ka main
Dhundun yoon jawab aise

Lakhon hazaron mein kya?
Mamuli kirdaro mein yaan
Aau inn khayalon mein main 
Banke kuch nayab aise

Tu hi hai aasmaan
Mere dil ko azmaan
Aasmaani taaron mein main
Dhundhu yoon apni jagah

Mere bhi khayalon mein tu
Duniya ke kinaro se yoon 
Pass mere 
Pass mein aaja
Aa ja na  

Chorus

Aa re aa x 8

Bridge

Sun toh

Ek din yeh dil mera 
Hoga benaqaab haan 
Aur phir tujhe nazar ayega 
Ki

Antariksh ki tarah 
Yeh hai behisaab sa
Aur sab tera yeh
ho jayega 
Hi

Para 3

Dil ke afsane mere 
Keh na paya saloon se main
Sochoon yeh khazane mere 
Bantoon sare aaj tujhse 

Bante bahane mere
Taloon kyun na jane kal pe?
Hoon jo ab main pass tere
Betha hoon naraaz khudse

Band hain taalon mein
Taloon sari baatein yeh
Taloon sari baatein kya mein 
Tere intezaar mein?

Rehta hoon umeedon mein kya?
Tu hi mujhko keh degi aa
Pass mere 
Pass mein aaja
Aa ja na  

Chorus

Aa re aa x 8

snippet.description:

Tere Bin Episode 45 - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - Digitally Presented by Nisa BB Cream - 17th May 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Tere Bin Digitally presented by Nisa BB Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab‚Äôs life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family‚Äôs decision regarding her and Murtasim‚Äôs life. Meerab‚Äôs hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab‚Äôs arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim‚Äôs family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq

snippet.title: EXTRACTION 2 | Official Hindi Trailer | Netflix India
snippet.description:
Taiyaar ho jaiye apne jeevan ki sabse romanchak safar ke liye! EXTRACTION 2 mein dekhiye Chris Hemsworth ko Tyler Rake ke avtaar main - Netflix par, 16 June.

Hemsworth reunites with director Sam Hargrave, with Joe and Anthony Russo's AGBO producing and Joe Russo writing. Golshifteh Farahani reprises her role from the first film, with Daniel Bernhardt and Tinatin Dalakishvili also co-starring.

This is a sequel to the first film that was based on the graphic novel 'Ciudad' by Ande Parks, from a story by Ande Parks, Joe Russo & Anthony Russo, with illustrations by Fernando Le√≥n Gonz√°lez. EXTRACTION 2 is produced by Anthony Russo, Joe Russo, Mike Larocca, Chris Hemsworth, Patrick Newall and Sam Hargrave, with Angela Russo-Otstot, Jake Aust, Benjamin Grayson, Steven Scavelli, Christopher Markus and Stephen McFeely as executive producers.

Episode 3774: Kuch Pao Aur Kuch Kho
--------------------------------------------------------
Popatlal gets engrossed in his thoughts after Vinu Kaka tells him to change his name in order to get married. Madhavi and Bhide discuss Popatlal's decision about alternating his names. Popatlal discusses the same with his boss, and he suggests Popatlal not change his name. Popatlal decides to ask Jetha about this. So he visits Gada Electronics. Meanwhile, Nattu Kaka and Bagha get excited due to the massive sales. While Jetha is at his godown, he gets a call from Bagha that someone special from Gokhuldham has come to meet him. Jetha gets excited thinking about Babita. Stay tuned!¬†

#pakistaneconomy #indvspak #abhiandniyu 

Welcome to our YouTube channel, where we delve into pressing global issues. In this video, we explore the economic crisis currently plaguing Pakistan, examining its causes, impacts, and potential solutions.

Pakistan, a country with a rich cultural heritage and immense potential, has been grappling with economic challenges in recent years. Understanding the complexities of this crisis is crucial to formulating effective strategies for recovery and sustainable development.

In this video, we provide a comprehensive analysis of the causes behind the Pakistani economic crisis. Factors such as a growing population, inadequate infrastructure, political instability, corruption, and a high fiscal deficit have all contributed to the country's economic woes. We delve into each of these elements to offer you a deeper understanding of their impact on Pakistan's economy.

Moreover, we shed light on the far-reaching consequences of the economic crisis on various sectors and the lives of ordinary Pakistanis. Rising inflation, unemployment, poverty, and an increasing debt burden have put immense strain on the population, exacerbating social and economic inequalities. By exploring these effects, we aim to highlight the urgency of finding sustainable solutions.

Our video doesn't stop at identifying the challenges; we also explore potential solutions to address the Pakistani economic crisis. From implementing structural reforms to promoting investment and entrepreneurship, we discuss strategies that could revitalize the economy and pave the way for long-term growth and stability.

Join us as we navigate through the intricacies of the Pakistani economic crisis and empower ourselves with knowledge about this critical issue. By understanding the root causes, impacts, and potential solutions, we can collectively contribute to the ongoing discussions and efforts aimed at overcoming this crisis.

Don't forget to like, comment, and share this video to spread awareness about the Pakistani economic crisis and the importance of finding sustainable solutions. Subscribe to our channel for more thought-provoking content on global issues. Together, let's explore and work towards a brighter future for Pakistan and its people.

A boy came out of the house eager to know the history of old days. After passing a long way, he appeared in front of a big mountain. Hearing the name of this hill from the village people, he understood that the treasure of Emperor Ashoka was hidden here. Entering the mountain cave, he saw something written in an unknown language on a door. But is this writing a puzzle to reach the place where the treasure is kept? Can the boy recover the treasure of Emperor Ashoka?

snippet.title: FAST X | Final Trailer
snippet.description:
The end of the road begins Friday. Watch the FINAL TRAILER Now. #FASTX 

Get tickets now: https://tickets.fastxmovie.com/

The end of the road begins. 

Fast X, the tenth film in the Fast & Furious Saga, launches the final chapters of one of cinema‚Äôs most storied and popular global franchises, now in its third decade and still going strong with the same core cast and characters as when it began.

Over many missions and against impossible odds, Dom Toretto (Vin Diesel) and his family have outsmarted, out-nerved and outdriven every foe in their path. Now, they confront the most lethal opponent they‚Äôve ever faced: A terrifying threat emerging from the shadows of the past who‚Äôs fueled by blood revenge, and who is determined to shatter this family and destroy everything‚Äîand everyone‚Äîthat Dom loves, forever.  
 
In 2011‚Äôs Fast Five, Dom and his crew took out nefarious Brazilian drug kingpin Hernan Reyes and decapitated his empire on a bridge in Rio De Janeiro. What they didn‚Äôt know was that Reyes‚Äô son, Dante (Aquaman‚Äôs Jason Momoa), witnessed it all and has spent the last 12 years masterminding a plan to make Dom pay the ultimate price. 
 
Dante‚Äôs plot will scatter Dom‚Äôs family from Los Angeles to the catacombs of Rome, from Brazil to London and from Portugal to Antarctica. New allies will be forged and old enemies will resurface. But everything changes when Dom discovers that his own 8-year-old son (Leo Abelo Perry, Black-ish) is the ultimate target of Dante‚Äôs vengeance. 
 
Directed by Louis Leterrier (Clash of the Titans, The Incredible Hulk), Fast X stars returning cast members Michelle Rodriguez, Tyrese Gibson, Chris ‚ÄúLudacris‚Äù Bridges, Nathalie Emmanuel, Jordana Brewster, Sung Kang, Jason Statham, John Cena and Scott Eastwood, with Oscar¬Æ winner Helen Mirren and Oscar¬Æ winner Charlize Theron. 
 
The film also features an extraordinary new cast including Oscar¬Æ winner Brie Larson as Tess, a rogue representative from the Agency; Alan Richtson (Reacher) as Aimes, the new head of the Agency who doesn‚Äôt hold the same fondness for Dom‚Äôs crew as his predecessor, Mr. Nobody; Daniela Melchior (The Suicide Squad) as a Brazilian street racer with a powerful tie to Dom‚Äôs past; and legendary Oscar¬Æ winner Rita Moreno as Dom and Mia‚Äôs Abuelita Toretto. 
 
Fast X is produced by Neal H. Moritz, Vin Diesel, Justin Lin, Jeff Kirschenbaum and Samantha Vincent. The executive producers are Joseph M. Caracciolo, Jr., David Cain, Chris Morgan, Amanda Lewis and Mark Bomback. www.thefastsaga.com

Official Website: https://www.fastxmovie.com/
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/TheFastSaga
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/TheFastSaga
Twitter: https://twitter.com/TheFastSaga
TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@thefastsaga

Over many missions and against impossible odds, Dom Toretto (Vin Diesel) and his family have outsmarted, out-nerved and outdriven every foe in their path. Now, they confront the most lethal opponent they‚Äôve ever faced: A terrifying threat emerging from the shadows of the past who‚Äôs fueled by blood revenge, and who is determined to shatter this family and destroy everything‚Äîand everyone‚Äîthat Dom loves, forever.  
 
In 2011‚Äôs Fast Five, Dom and his crew took out nefarious Brazilian drug kingpin Hernan Reyes and decapitated his empire on a bridge in Rio De Janeiro. What they didn‚Äôt know was that Reyes‚Äô son, Dante (Aquaman‚Äôs Jason Momoa), witnessed it all and has spent the last 12 years masterminding a plan to make Dom pay the ultimate price. 
 
Dante‚Äôs plot will scatter Dom‚Äôs family from Los Angeles to the catacombs of Rome, from Brazil to London and from Portugal to Antarctica. New allies will be forged and old enemies will resurface. But everything changes when Dom discovers that his own 8-year-old son (Leo Abelo Perry, Black-ish) is the ultimate target of Dante‚Äôs vengeance. 
 
Directed by Louis Leterrier (Clash of the Titans, The Incredible Hulk), Fast X stars returning cast members Michelle Rodriguez, Tyrese Gibson, Chris ‚ÄúLudacris‚Äù Bridges, Nathalie Emmanuel, Jordana Brewster, Sung Kang, Jason Statham, John Cena and Scott Eastwood, with Oscar¬Æ winner Helen Mirren and Oscar¬Æ winner Charlize Theron. 
 
The film also features an extraordinary new cast including Oscar¬Æ winner Brie Larson as Tess, a rogue representative from the Agency; Alan Richtson (Reacher) as Aimes, the new head of the Agency who doesn‚Äôt hold the same fondness for Dom‚Äôs crew as his predecessor, Mr. Nobody; Daniela Melchior (The Suicide Squad) as a Brazilian street racer with a powerful tie to Dom‚Äôs past; and legendary Oscar¬Æ winner Rita Moreno as Dom and Mia‚Äôs Abuelita Toretto. 
 
Fast X is produced by Neal H. Moritz, Vin Diesel, Justin Lin, Jeff Kirschenbaum and Samantha Vincent. The executive producers are Joseph M. Caracciolo, Jr., David Cain, Chris Morgan, Amanda Lewis and Mark Bomback. www.thefastsaga.com
